title: Texas state representative introduces bill to vote on secession
description: The bill allows Texas to explore the possibility of secession and present plans to the state legislature. If passed, the referendum will be placed on the ballot in 2024.

title: Atlanta 'Cop City' protest quickly turns violent and fiery, video shows
description: Atlanta Police posted video showing rioters storm the future site of a public safety and training center, before throwing rocks and fireworks, and setting equipment on fire.

title: Camila, Matthew McConaughey's kids make rare red carpet appearance at Paris Fashion Week
description: Matthew McConaughey's wife, Camila Alves McConaughey, was joined by the couple's oldest two children during a rare appearance on the red carpet during Paris Fashion Week.

title: Car pulled from Arkansas lake contained body of person missing since 2008
description: Police in Arkansas discovered a submerged vehicle in Lake Hamilton containing the body of an individual linked to a February 2008 missing persons report.

title: Southern Poverty Law Center lawyer arrested, charged with domestic terrorism amid Atlanta 'Cop City' attack
description: A lawyer for the Southern Poverty Law Center was reportedly arrested and charged with domestic terrorism in connection to the violence that broke out in Atlanta over "Cop City."

title: GOP erupts after Americans missing in Mexico: 'Cartels couldn’t ask for a better partner in crime than' Biden
description: Republicans are pointing the finger at President Biden's border policies after four Americans were kidnapped in Mexico Friday after crossing the border from Texas.

title: Biden punting on Alaska oil project would hurt union jobs, help Iran: Rick Perry
description: President Biden's administration is set to decide whether to open up a potentially massive oil drilling project on Alaska's North Slope in the coming days.

title: MSNBC analyst whitewashes COVID 'conspiracy theory' lab leak stance: 'Always' took it seriously
description: MSNBC's John Heilemann offered a stunning reversal on the COVID lab leak theory during his Friday night panel appearance on "Real Time with Bill Maher."
